metadata.name: Darkness
metadata.description:
How afraid of the darkness?

I thought I wasn't afraid until my life became uncertain for the first time. Uncertainty is a huge black hole that swallows you whole! I guess I should admit that I'm 31 years old and the things I've always wanted to do for the sake of my dreams were crystal clear. 

I would draw and desire a specific roadmap. If you have patience and perseverance, I believe you can call it done!

PS: You can't even fall in love if you're that radical!

This photo belongs to these days when I have overcome my radicalism and come out of my darkness!

'' In the deep darkness, only the person sees the light.''  â€” Chuang Tzu
